# NuttyBliss – Chocolate & Nuts Store Website (plan.md)

## 1. Project Overview

* **Brand Name:** NuttyBliss
* **Tagline:** Pure Indulgence in Every Bite
* **Business Type:** Online Chocolate & Premium Nuts Store
* **Target Audience:** Kids, teens, families, gift buyers, health‑conscious customers, corporate clients

### Unique Selling Points (USP)

* Premium chocolates + healthy nuts in one store
* Customizable gift boxes & festive hampers
* Budget‑friendly to luxury collections
* Freshness‑guaranteed products
* Multi‑language, easy‑to‑use website

